236_d535d91f3baaaf490250e7110550fb56.jpg&h=3d0dbaeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本 KEMCO 宣佈酒場經營 RPG 《馬雷尼亞國的冒險酒場（マレニア国の冒険酒場）》（iOS/Android）今日（4月25日）Android版本正式配信，iOS版本預計5月配信。<br />\n<br />\n本作是一款結合料理製作與地城戰鬥的酒場經營 RPG，玩家要透過討伐魔物、垂釣畜牧等手段，收集食材，並將之製成菜餚，填滿客人的胃袋，而中出現的料理種類，更超過600種或以上。</div>"},{"pid":"d91a36ec06f6c39f1cc7ac1b22245428c110eae4","tid":642112,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50b209ea166eb26607e03a255d111b4cb79e9e5","tid":642112,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91a36ec06f6c39f1cc7ac1b22245428c110eae4","tid":642112,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a80fa23af6afba7b24ff9f83db8968c769d5f8","tid":642112,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"個topic 長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02efc0b6d0b0a1eb0479d4c36b924cfb0645dcc5","tid":642112,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a80fa23af6afba7b24ff9f83db8968c769d5f8","tid":642112,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"個topic 長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431be905a3b5cbbf92249a54bf4f6202f63a1a7f","tid":642112,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"原來未有ios <br />\n我出返去先"},{"pid":"0c27c797eb52e4d3d3eda5c18094508367328082","tid":642112,"uid":22579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl